<plot>After being ridiculed for losing his team's basketball game due to his weight, Chris can't seem to accept his physicality. His friend Sarah likes him for who he is, but Chris' lack of self-confidence keeps him from pursuing his love interest. Fat Kid Luv is the story of the difficulty of accepting yourself and others when you are different from society's standards.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190490</url></doc>
